{
  "texts": [
    "Proposed method Module architectureYOLOv8 is an advanced deep-learning model that further enhances the capabilities of YOLOv5 in the object detection field.",
    "It incorporates a range of network structures and utilizes C2F modules to enhance YOLOv5.",
    "The CSP modules effectively reduce parameters and FLOPs while maintaining accuracy.",
    "Additionally, YOLOv8 introduces a new anchor box generator that considers the distribution of object sizes in the dataset.",
    "In this study, YOLOv8-CAB, a method based on YOLOv8, has been proposed."
  ]
}